Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们悄声无息地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界真正的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这单片眼镜借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称为「坂井悠二」的人类究竟是不是火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请自己去确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要现在你来协助我们看来是没可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小姐这样在这个城市土生土长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留着这个城市纯粹的印象的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才适合进行调律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是火炬的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学没事的…一定没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天的祭典上一定要对坂井同学说「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}破碎的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把目标放在悠二身上的「扮装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混进这城市里的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里原本已经不平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变得更糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不能再待在这城市里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有「扮装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天必须和母亲以及大家分别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想暂时在这里…和平时一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天穿上和服让悠二大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了离开这里的时候也…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起离开这城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  这还真是迷得彻底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们  应该明白这意味着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的目标就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能使用这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就带我们走是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不是绕着圈子叫我们别跟去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换作平时的你不就一顿臭揍了结的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来明天会下酒雨咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 祭典穿不穿和服去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为买新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说要离开这城市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天5点在桥那里碰头怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那小姑娘如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫坂井悠二的男人不是火炬便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能冷静到可以帮忙的程度就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调律这城市稍微有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 歪曲得异常严重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在这附近也打上印记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再打一两个应该够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 不光是歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有某些不协和感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止可谓是一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离准备完成还剩6小时14分32秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这花纹非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见这么漂亮的小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠真得会吓一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小悠好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经有离开城市的心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经那么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六一直是下午开始锻炼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会早回来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他说过今天晚上开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去祭典的事没告诉过他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是闲逛去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去找小悠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和池他们在缘日玩也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}缘日：参拜神佛的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下便条的话就算错过也不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里遇见的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠会更吃惊也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠缘日来的话绝对会买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吃看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要妨碍我们训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是来祭典玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人说要出门的话就乖乖跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊  再那样继续的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会做出一道难看的活「人」刺身咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣太  去买点酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝酒么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方 走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有苹果糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道…坂井同学到底有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…这样下去就…永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剩下的就是等待那位小姐的协助了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  仍然很介意这不协和感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是歪曲太厉害的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有红世之徒的气息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止还没有办法对付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真~~~是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类还真好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一个火焰之雾都没察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授  准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就对坂井同学好好说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都没任何气息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草 我想起还有件事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但放出了自在式却没有气息是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概藏在什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 放松心情就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们去玻璃檀就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要查出红世之徒的位置就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全给看穿了呵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用法已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不是真打算带他们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是临时应急用用罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说也需要用玻璃檀来调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这自在式还真大手笔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设下这么大的机关  看来不是普通人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二也一定察觉到了 到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先要通知夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…坂井同学…骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么吉田一美会和悠二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吉田同学知道了我是火炬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧  红世之徒开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须对吉田同学解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二一定要和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要对吉田一美那种人解释
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无关？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉田一美毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都没所谓啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到夏娜会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说并不是无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「仪装的收集者」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好久不见了呢「天壤之劫火」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也被这自在式…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸子西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总对这乱七八糟的自在式有不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…「探耽求究」——旦塔里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那个神经病教授没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那家伙的气息完~~全感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来更加需要玻璃檀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧一点吧  启作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中那家伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绪什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才和你在一起的女人的事就不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了只是认识而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在蒙混了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…小绪 我可要生气咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我介意啊…非常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说到底为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喜欢田中荣太！所以才介意呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是…火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学  到底谁把这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世之徒的攻击可已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 继续刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这自在式使得歪曲更厉害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市将会被严重到不能修复的歪曲给吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为了什么而这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有对策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只要开始调律就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要的印记已经打完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需一位能将城市正常姿态印象化的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 实际上已经有心目中的人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微出了点纰漏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫作吉田一美的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她身上带着的气息原来是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她来的话调律马上就能开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为火焰之雾的使命会好好完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该是火焰之雾们来捣乱的时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 开始着手第二作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法马上给你答复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  待会会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在封绝中还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 必须做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能办到么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…紫？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  热闹起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后会变成什么样还真令人期待啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.74,0:24:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仍旧无法捕捉到教授的行踪之际
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.17,0:24:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「魂之圣庙」正在御崎市上空逐渐完成
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.04,0:24:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜作为火焰之雾而战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.44,0:24:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉着逐渐远去悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.22,0:24:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 在战斗之中
